Conte on Wilshere dive and Wenger: &quot;If I want I could talk about the refereeing decisions for one month but I don't want to do this because we must have respect for refereeing decisions. [Wenger] He has to accept the decisions&quot;<br />
<br />
Conte on managers talking about him: &quot;It is very strange because I don't like to speak about other coaches and other players. I think this is a form of respect that you must have. Sometimes Wenger forgets that in the last few games (against them) we finished with 10 men&quot;

